The Form Three student of Murichu Secondary School, identified as Samuel Migwi, is accused of assaulting teacher James Gikonyo.The incident is one of several similar ones in counties including Kisii, Nyamira and Vihiga. Police in Ndaragwa, Nyandarua County, are holding a 20-year-old student for allegedly attacking a teacher.
The Form Three student of Murichu Secondary School is accused of assaulting teacher James Gikonyo.
The Monday incident followed scolding of the student by Mr Gikonyo for jumping the queue as students were being served lunch.



